ri\\u00eancia na \\u00e1rea comercial e conhecimentos intermedi\\u00e1rios do Pacote Office. Ingl\\u00eas intermedi\\u00e1rio \\u00e9 desej\\u00e1vel.\\r\\n\\r\\nO que obter\\u00e1 em troca\\r\\n\\r\\nTer\\u00e1 um sal\\u00e1rio compat\\u00edvel com o mercado, assim como todo suporte para ajud\\u00e1-lo a ser bem sucedido na sua fun\\u00e7\\u00e3o.\\r\\n\\r\\nO que precisa fazer agora\\r\\n\\r\\nSe estiver interessado nesta posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o, clique \\\"Aplicar-se agora\\\" para encaminhar uma c\\u00f3pia atualizada do seu CV, ou entre em contato conosco agora.\\r\\n\\r\\nSe esta posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o n\\u00e3o for ideal para voc\\u00ea, mas estiver buscando por uma nova posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o, por favor conta-nos para discutirmos confidencialmente sobre a sua carreira.\",\"post_title\":\"Executivo de vendas\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"dffdsa\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-07-10 11:41:20\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-07-10 14:41:20\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/lajeado360.com\\/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=161\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":78,\"post_author\":\"4\",\"post_date\":\"2018-06-09 20:39:46\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2018-06-09 23:39:46\",\"post_content\":\"Your new company\\r\\n\\r\\nHays is the leading global professional recruiting group, experts at recruiting qualified, professional and skilled people globally. We are the world\\u2019s leading and UK\\u2019s largest recruiting specialists. With over 10.000 staff operating from 250 offices in 33 countries across 20 specialisms. Due to the continued success of our Offices in Brazil (Sao Paulo, Campinas, Rio de Janeiro), we are looking for an exceptional 360\\u00b0 Recruitment Consultant to add to our team.\\r\\n\\r\\nYour new role\\r\\n\\r\\nAs a 360\\u00b0 Recruitment Consultant at Hays you will manage the complete recruitment process. You will be responsible for winning new clients as well as maintaining and developing further relationships with existing clients, through both telephone and face to face meetings. You will be sourcing and meeting new candidates, through various means including advertising and networking. You\\u2019ll also maintain regular contact with existing candidates using our market leading database, whilst consistently hitting KPI\\u2019s and targets.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhat you\\u2019ll need to succeed\\r\\n\\r\\nYou will have a proven track record of success in previous employment, university or education and will thrive working in our high performance, corporate sales environment. You\\u2019ll demonstrate your exceptional interpersonal skills and the ability to deal in a professional manner with your clients and candidates, whilst also building relationships. You will be ambitious and driven to progress your career through demonstrating your inquisitive nature and thirst for knowledge, also you need to be passionate and interested in develop your industry. As well as possessing both excellent written and verbal communication skills, you will have attention to detail with a strong work ethic to achieve successful results. For this position we are looking for people with 1 to 3 years of experience as 360\\u00b0 Recruitment Consultant.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhat you\\u2019ll get in return\\r\\n\\r\\nHays are committed to developing our employees through our industry, leading training to help you achieve success as a Recruitment Consultant. You will be given the tools and resources to develop your sales and recruiting expertise in order for you to achieve and enjoy a lasting and rewarding recruitment career. You\\u2019ll enjoy working in our fast paced, challenging yet supportive and sociable environment. Hays believes in meritocracy and your success will be rewarded with a competitive salary, plus uncapped commission and wide range of flexible benefits and incentives. As an exceptional consultant, you will have the opportunity to progress your career through our meritocratic culture, moving into team and business management in the future.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhat you need to do now\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you want to work for the world\\u2019s leading recruiting experts as a 360\\u00b0 Recruitment Consultant click \\u2018apply now\\u2019 via the link below.\",\"post_title\":\"Experienced 360\\u00ba Recruitment Consultant\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"publish\",\"comment_status\":\"closed\",\"ping_status\":\"closed\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"nenhum-nao-eh-londres-5-vaga-do-candidato\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2018-07-10 11:38:02\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2018-07-10 14:38:02\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"https:\\/\\/lajeado360.com\\/vaga\\/nenhum-nao-eh-londres-5-vaga-do-candidato\\/\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"job_listing\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},{\"ID\":59,\"post_author\":\"1\",\"post_date\":\"2018-06-02 19:49:16\",\"post_date_gmt\":\"2018-06-02 22:49:16\",\"post_content\":\"    Disponibilidade para viagens pelo RS;\\r\\n\\r\\n    Experi\\u00eancia comercial em gest\\u00e3o de grandes contas.\\r\\n\\r\\nSobre nosso cliente\\r\\n\\r\\nNosso cliente \\u00e9 uma multinacional do segmento de bens de consumo.\\r\\nDescri\\u00e7\\u00e3o do cargo\\r\\n\\r\\nRealiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o do planejamento anual da conta;\\r\\n\\r\\nTrabalhar oportunidades de neg\\u00f3cios;\\r\\n\\r\\nGarantir a execu\\u00e7\\u00e3o do plano de neg\\u00f3cio da conta;\\r\\n\\r\\nPrestar o melhor atendimento ao cliente e realizar a gest\\u00e3o completa da conta.\\r\\nO candidato\\r\\n\\r\\n    Ensino Superior Completo;\\r\\n    Experi\\u00eancias anteriores na \\u00e1rea comercial;\\r\\n    Gest\\u00e3o de grandes contas;\\r\\n    Disponibilidade de viagens pelo R