nt Consultant to add to our team.\r\n\r\nYour new role\r\n\r\nAs a 360 Recruitment Consultant at Hays you will manage the complete recruitment process. You will be responsible for winning new clients as well as maintaining and developing further relationships with existing clients, through both telephone and face to face meetings. You will be sourcing and meeting new candidates, through various means including advertising and networking. Youll also maintain regular contact with existing candidates using our market leading database, whilst consistently hitting KPIs and targets.\r\n\r\nWhat youll need to succeed\r\n\r\nYou will have a proven track record of success in previous employment, university or education and will thrive working in our high performance, corporate sales environment. Youll demonstrate your exceptional interpersonal skills and the ability to deal in a professional manner with your clients and candidates, whilst also building relationships. You will be ambitious and driven to progress your career through demonstrating your inquisitive nature and thirst for knowledge, also you need to be passionate and interested in develop your industry. As well as possessing both excellent written and verbal communication skills, you will have attention to detail with a strong work ethic to achieve successful results. For this position we are looking for people with 1 to 3 years of experience as 360 Recruitment Consultant.\r\n\r\nWhat youll get in return\r\n\r\nHays are committed to developing our employees through our industry, leading training to help you achieve success as a Recruitment Consultant. You will be given the tools and resources to develop your sales and recruiting expertise in order for you to achieve and enjoy a lasting and rewarding recruitment career. Youll enjoy working in our fast paced, challenging yet supportive and sociable environment. Hays believes in meritocracy and your success will be rewarded with a competitive salary, plus uncapped commission and wide range of flexible benefits and incentives. As an exceptional consultant, you will have the opportunity to progress your career through our meritocratic culture, moving into team and business management in the future.\r\n\r\nWhat you need to do now\r\n\r\nIf you want to work for the worlds leading recruiting experts as a 360 Recruitment Consultant click apply now via the link below.','Experienced 360 Recruitment Consultant','','publish','closed','closed','','nenhum-nao-eh-londres-5-vaga-do-candidato','','','2018-07-10 11:38:02','2018-07-10 14:38:02','',0,'https://lajeado360.com/vaga/nenhum-nao-eh-londres-5-vaga-do-candidato/',0,'job_listing','',0),(79,1,'2018-06-09 21:02:33','2018-06-10 00:02:33','','CadastrarCurrculo','','publish','closed','closed','','cadastrar-curriculo','','','2018-07-10 00:11:47','2018-07-10 03:11:47','',0,'http://lajeado360.com/?p=79',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(84,1,'2018-06-11 20:15:17','2018-06-11 23:15:17','','Front Page','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2018-06-11 20:15:17','2018-06-11 23:15:17','',13,'http://lajeado360.com/2018/06/11/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(83,1,'2018-06-11 20:02:43','2018-06-11 23:02:43','<div id=\"overlapable-2\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Overlapable\" data-id=\"stripped-coloured-icon-boxes\" data-category=\"overlapable\" class=\"features-coloured-icon-boxes-section\" data-overlap=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"gridContainer\">\r\n<div class=\"features-coloured-icon-boxes-innerrow flexbox-list dark-text\" data-type=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"features-coloured-icon-boxes-featurecol cp3cols\">\r\n<div class=\"features-coloured-icon-boxes-iconcontainer\" data-content-item-container=\"true\"><i class=\"features-coloured-icon fa fa-bolt\" data-cp-fa=\"true\"></i></div>\r\n<h4 class=\"\">Responsive Design</h4>\r\n<p class=\"\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p>\r\n